{% extends '/materialize/layout/base.twig' %}

{% block title %}Announcement regarding your personal data{% endblock %}

{% block body %}

    <main class="container announcement_container">
        <header class="pt-5">
            <img class="synoint_logo" src="{{ asset('build/images/syno_logo.png') }}" alt="synoint" />
        </header>

        <h2 class="mt-5">
            Announcement regarding your
            <span class="flow_text"> personal data</span>
        </h2>
        <section class="row pt-5 justify">
            <div class="col s6 pr-5">
                <h5 class="m-0">About us</h5>
                <p>
                    SynoInt is a group of companies (which consists of UAB Syno
                    International (parent company) and Syno Japan Inc. (Syno Japan),
                    Syno Poland sp. zo.o. (Syno Poland), Asia Syno International PTE.
                    LTD. (Syno Asia) and Syno International Inc. (Syno Korea)
                    (subsidiaries)) which provide data collection, processing, reporting
                    and reward solutions.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Due to the fact that SynoInt processes your personal data, we note
                    that your privacy is the most important and natural matter in our
                    company and we will process your personal data in a reliable,
                    legitimate and the most secure way.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Please be advised that as of May 25, 2018 throughout the European
                    Union (EU) and other countries that voluntarily joins and declares
                    compliance, the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) will be
                    directly applicable, which aims - to ensure a strong and unified
                    data protection standards. In this regard, we are responsibly
                    preparing for application of GDPR and treat your personal data
                    entrusted to us very carefully. Our goal is to continue to be your
                    reliable partner, so we ask you to review, get acquainted and agree
                    to our prepared legal documents related to the processing of your
                    personal data.
                </p>

                <p>
                    We also kindly ask you to follow the terms and conditions referred
                    in the documents.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="col s6 pr-4">
                <h5 class="m-0">Your consent and permission</h5>
                <p>
                    By clicking "Accept", you agree and confirm permission that SynoInt
                    processes your personal data and you confirm your consent that you
                    have read, got acquainted, understood and do not disagree to
                    personal data processing operations and objectives of SynoInt that
                    are defined in the following legal documents:
                </p>

                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <a href="https://www.synoint.com/privacy-policy/" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a>
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        <a href="https://www.synoint.com/security-policy/" target="_blank">Security Policy</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="https://www.synoint.com/cookies-policy/" target="_blank">Cookies Policy</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="https://www.synoint.com/dpo/" target="_blank">Data Protection Officers</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="https://www.synoint.com/terms-of-use/" target="_blank">Terms of Use</a>
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        <a href="https://www.synoint.com/quality-documentation/" target="_blank">
                            Quality documentation</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    Your consent can be easily cancelled at any time by writing an email
                    to:
                </p>

                <ul class="ml-4">
                    <li>
                        <a href="mailto:data.protection@synoint.com" target="_blank">
                            data.protection@synoint.com
                        </a>
                        (If it is related to the processing of personal data)
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="mailto:info@synoint.com" target="_blank">
                            info@synoint.com
                        </a>
                        (If there is a contractual relationship with SynoInt).
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <div class="mt-5 btn_container">
                    {{
                        form_row(
                            form.accept,
                            {
                                'attr': {'class': 'btn btn_border waves-effect waves-default'},
                                'label': 'Accept'
                            }
                        )
                    }}
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>


    </main>

{% endblock %}
